{#
name: Binding HTTP Client
description: Declarative HTTP binding template with simplified tools syntax
tags: [integration, binding, http, declarative]
parameters:
  - name: skill_name
    type: str
    description: Skill display name
    required: true
  - name: skill_description
    type: str
    description: Brief description of the integration purpose
    required: true
  - name: base_url
    type: str
    description: API base URL (e.g. https://api.example.com)
    required: true
  - name: token_env
    type: str
    description: Environment variable for API token
    default: "API_TOKEN"
examples:
  - "HTTP binding skill for order query"
  - "Declarative API integration without Python handler"
#}
---
name: {{ skill_name | kebab_case }}
description: {{ skill_description }}
owlclaw:
  prerequisites:
    env:
      - {{ token_env }}
tools:
  fetch-resource:
    description: Fetch one resource by id
    resource_id: string
    binding:
      type: http
      method: GET
      url: {{ base_url }}/resources/{resource_id}
      headers:
        Authorization: Bearer ${{ "{" }}{{ token_env }}{{ "}" }}
---
# {{ skill_name }} — 使用指南

## 目标

{{ skill_description }}

## 运行方式

1. 在环境变量中设置 `{{ token_env }}`。
2. 使用 `fetch-resource` 读取目标资源。
3. 根据返回结果给出业务结论。

## 注意事项

- 所有敏感信息使用 `${ENV_VAR}` 引用，不要写明文 token。
- 如果需要写操作，先将 binding `mode` 设为 `shadow` 做对比验证。
